<subSubSection id="CF0A12A3D7BEB968E93B9E5888C80110" pageId="null" pageNumber="462" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="08374C4DCB53D30CA5E6912EB72467AE" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Italienische Spitzklette</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="ABA8E4090EC5FDE4395FB3BBCC423A04" pageId="null" pageNumber="462" type="description">
<paragraph id="27081DC038912BF9CA09EE09575C17BF" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="09811E4E2B790BDD6FA7C35FEAE2049B" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Xanthium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="462" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="strumarium">
<emphasis id="BC93CAC4081B6BC2904AB0A67C5E5464" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">X. strumarium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="493B27A6C64EC4C3E18CA8B3FE609DA9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">
Stengel mit kleinen braunen Flecken; 
<normalizedToken id="CB2DC97A69016381E056B3F258AE0986" originalValue="Fruchtköpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Fruchtkoepfe</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="FEF4F25D9C995794D0CB273154790F06" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">
<normalizedToken id="4B2F0A6FD5034F783F11DB956B5228FA" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
mit 
<normalizedToken id="C0563B3FADF8CAEF89164FFCA9055D50" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Huelle</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
) 
<emphasis id="CDA2189B65299A043082A240F9B67D42" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">20</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="D5196B5FC3517329937EDD314ED9DDE8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">30 mm lang, mit 4</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="5BD66534AE65871831F72E32FED9E90C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">6 mm langen Stacheln besetzt.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="4EFABE45EC5E5D6ED48F33D2A48D4E3A" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="B8FA8073534FF138C15BBCD18CD8CC7E" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
Sommer und Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4E268D7FC0D1F8D9AA21FD5A72058542" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">
<emphasis id="6A9E4034B7EF80FF26BF7674DDC6893B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="7719E2947210869F5DDA89EF0BDCD85B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">36:</emphasis>
Material aus Kanada (Symons 1926).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2D2C157E84A30820F519FB4690DC5E36" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">
<emphasis id="DEF4B061FA7B1A32816B6C4159978C4F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. 
<normalizedToken id="B95811EEE515E8F477383A55D0FE1440" originalValue="Ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName id="F34154D4F750326E097600041BB6EBAB" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Xanthium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="null" pageNumber="462" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="strumarium">
<emphasis id="FF7D5E05B03FB3817DEA63C2618E3465" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">X. strumarium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="222F440BFA1D34C83C33CC170E95DB58" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">
<emphasis id="3DF7215EE690611444510713CE96C0FF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Wahrscheinlich 
<normalizedToken id="4843FDDD5EC85382C8C3F143C71C0678" originalValue="ursprünglich" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">urspruenglich</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="97691DC2331BD7505F7AAEAF3D4FAA9A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">amerikanische Pflanze.</emphasis>
Heute 
<normalizedToken id="287BAEC0F32DA7E59C3816AC664FFA85" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">ueber</normalizedToken>
weite Gebiete der Erde verbreitet. - Im Gebiet: Poebene, Tessin; ziemlich selten und 
<normalizedToken id="0DFC7E235CD99BCAEE18897699E87995" originalValue="unbeständig" pageId="null" pageNumber="462">unbestaendig</normalizedToken>
; selten auch adventiv.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
